text: Hanna Jarkiewicz (born 31 August 1954) is a Polish rower. She competed in the women's double sculls event at the 1980 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1954 births Category:Living people Category:Polish female rowers Category:Olympic rowers of Poland Category:Rowers at the 1980 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Wrocław
